# Worklog Discipline

When making meaningful changes, update `WORKLOG.md` before final handoff.

## Update Required For
- Behavior changes
- Architecture or implementation pattern changes
- Process/governance updates

## Entry Expectations
- Newest entry at top
- Include goal, file-level changes, notes/decisions, follow-ups
- Keep entries specific and grep-friendly
